com.nearinfinity.honeycomb.hbase.rowkey
Class IndexRowKeyBuilder

java.lang.Object
  com.nearinfinity.honeycomb.hbase.rowkey.IndexRowKeyBuilder

public class IndexRowKeyBuilder
extends Object

A builder for creating IndexRowKey instances. Builder instances can be reused as it is safe to call build() multiple times.
